Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:18.82,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}曾經想著總有人會解決
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:24.38,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}多少帶著旁觀的心態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:27.06,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:32.35,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請告訴不成熟的我們
